						<div class="postbody">I'm now thinking how to do a good scrolling engine and I've come with the doubt, is there any game with a status bar that scrolls 4 ways AND has more than 2 screens of height?
<br />Super Mario bros 3 And Kyrby mess with nametable bits at $2000 to show the statusbar via irq I think, but that way you cant have more than 2 screens + statusbar of height.
<br />Any ideas?</div>

