						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">Wave wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Mmm, I really don't understand RC Pro-Am. It only seems to use one screen from the two, maybe disables screen and draws statusbar at midframe?</div>
<br />It uses single screen mirroring. One of the name tables is used for gameplay, and the other for the status bar (which is selected when rendering reaches the bottom part of the screen).
<br />
<br />But if you didn't mind a few empty scanlines at the top of the status bar you sure could draw it wherever you wanted every frame.</div>

